{"tid":1489762,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Set死線？ 不了","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:43:49.000Z","uid":126115,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e03d2bab45a51f4496821b5f17f768b6b582599c","tid":1489762,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"818大家要五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n已經係好清晰咁表達左<br />\n今日林奠出黎記招依然當五大訴求視若目睹<br />\n我地再比多幾多時間佢都係唔會回應了<br />\nSet 死線？ 不了 今日就開始全面升級<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不<span style=\"color: red;\">指責 不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6ebc2e48feeb7c27b1437ef4426de8c07529439","tid":1489762,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"我想大家多d討論下一步升級既內容<br />\n香港政府係無權力同我地deal 5大訴求嫁<br />\n再多既遊行示威都唔會得到結果<br />\n我地要升級逼使政府停止我地既行動，例如罷交稅，拒絕警察執法，完全無視因抗爭帶來既法律問題，勇武自保"},{"pid":"be42edf026a76e583621399863fcb45473077e03","tid":1489762,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fbfe94263f46450c2a05133441c7eb407166f5","tid":1489762,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1303196eef5cd2c5814242476b79529a8528b5f9","tid":1489762,"uid":126115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebd158fd8dc620fb3360ced0a579d21fe1727f1","tid":1489762,"uid